    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Had no money, they paid for this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went to the yeshiva there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know the consul with whom I talked was very much interested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The American consul and the Canadian consul, they were very much interested, and people too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think they didn't want to hear much of the war, because they were afraid in America they might have to enter the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, there was this kind of sentiment, you see, don't mix in, the Monroe Doctrine.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
